00:12:50,760 --> 00:12:58,600
And so setting up a specific form that says exactly the questions that we need answered

168
00:12:58,600 --> 00:13:04,840
and in what way they need to be answered can help ease a lot of back and forth of, oh,

169
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:06,120
hey, what was this thing again?

