00:13:10,640 --> 00:13:12,600
Wait, what?

172
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:20,200
Instead, here's a nice form that eases that because it's exactly what we need in the

173
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:21,240
structure that we need it.

174
00:13:23,240 --> 00:13:32,200
And finally, a tool that probably you think of more coming from sort of business world,

175
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:34,040
but can actually be really helpful in academia.

